Henry Brelie, appellee, v. David. Saul Klafter and Amanda E. Klafter, appellants.Gen. No. 32,815.Heard in the first division of this court for the first district at the June term, 1928.

Hatchett, J., dissenting.

Opinion filed February 11, 1929.Additional opinion filed February 27, 1929.Perlman, Goodman & Scolnik, for appellants. Loueks, Eckert & Peterson, for appellee. Mr. Presiding Justice O’Connor

delivered the opinion of the court.
